{"tid":399194,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[友情,勝利,熱血]異世界冒險故事-迷宮探索者","createTime":"2017-09-13T17:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T02:38:58.000Z","uid":15954,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"db6f529802c414d6632b93ca015d0ab10de87dfc","tid":399194,"uid":15954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:52:51.000Z","msg":"原作係WEB版小說,之後推出過2次書<br />\n內容係主角同埋佢既同學比創世神為左解悶而掉去異世界<br />\n從而展開佢地壯大既冒險故事<br />\n故事途中,佢地之間出現左分歧,最後成員各散東西<br />\n而主角就決定負起攻略最強迷宮既職責<br />\n<br />\n總結,故事雖然教唔到我咩大道理,但非常之有親切感<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786b0697b607f7884d8782c803c21ebd9aaf42cf","tid":399194,"uid":21881,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:55:58.000Z","msg":"仲有6年先18歲 收藏住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee8a4c0f832b9226a50eb20f5e75e8eb94decd6","tid":399194,"uid":15954,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T17:57:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有6年先18歲 收藏住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁慘<br />\n咁可以睇住漫畫先<br />\n雖然無左好多劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef2d8a18d4f546fe5a418fb397ae9fb68d53ab2","tid":399194,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T18:00:57.000Z","msg":"我細細個已經follow樓主"},{"pid":"4f64a2c190537509f1331f3f85e35623e0c7683a","tid":399194,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T18:02:03.000Z","msg":"第5本男主本來可以搞掂個bitch<br />\n結果到頭來又係唔夠狠<br />\n<br />\n不過而家咁佢2個既關係都冇咩好寫啦"},{"pid":"72da79705848bae060044c97ab5cf032b0684a21","tid":399194,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T18:07:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第5本男主本來可以搞掂個bitch<br />\n結果到頭來又係唔夠狠<br />\n<br